item.title: Filco Minila Air
item.description: I like mechanical keyboards, I have a lot of them! I probably won’t have a life long enough to use all of them to their full life span, but when I saw Filco Minila Air for the first time, I wanted it to join my army of keyboards.

item.description: Hi there, I am Ye Liu. I am a software developer, who cannot live without Mac, Linux, and Vim, speaks JavaScript, Elm, Go, Elixir, Python and C, is passionate about web and mobile development, is crazy about things that are invisible but powerful.
